Node instructions:
sudo apt install nodejs
sudo apt install npm
sudo npm install -g n
sudo n 8.9.0
sudo n
sudo npm install -g npm@5.5.1 (need chmod +w?, se non funziona sudo /usr/bin/npm install -g npm...)
wget -qO - https://www.mongodb.org/static/pgp/server-4.2.asc | sudo apt-key add -
echo "deb [ arch=amd64,arm64 ] https://repo.mongodb.org/apt/ubuntu bionic/mongodb-org/4.2 multiverse" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/mongodb-org-4.2.list
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y mongodb-org

Start things:
sudo service mongod start (se non funziona qualcosa leggi /var/log/mongodb/mongod.log o rimuovi e ricrea /var/lib/mongodb)
mongo (per fare query)


Note:
usare issues di github per fare i lavori -> milestones === sprints


